a_keys
[TITLE]The Manual: Adventure Mode Key Bindings[/TITLE]
Here are the keys you can use to control your adventurer.
[B][B]
[C:7:0:1]Main Keys:[C:7:0:0]
[B]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UP]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWN]
[IKEY:CURSOR_LEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_RIGHT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UPLEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UPRIGHT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWNLEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWNRIGHT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UP_Z]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWN_Z] - Move/attack.
[B]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_SAME_SQUARE] - Attack same square.
[B]
[IKEY:A_WAIT] - Wait for a step.
[B]
[IKEY:SELECT] - Advance/clear messages.
[B]
[IKEY:A_ANNOUNCEMENTS] - View announcements.
[B]
[IKEY:A_COMPANIONS] - View companions.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INV_DROP] - Drop an item.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INV_EATDRINK] - Eat or drink something.
[B]
[IKEY:A_GROUND] - Pick up an item.
[B]
[IKEY:A_SHOOT] - Fire a projectile.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INV_LOOK] - Inventory.
[B]
[IKEY:A_LOOK] - Look around.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TALK] - Talk to somebody.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INV_PUTIN] - Put an item in a container.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INV_REMOVE] - Remove an item you are wearing or from a container.
[B]
[IKEY:A_STANCE] - Stand or lie down.
[B]
[IKEY:A_THROW] - Throw an item.
[B]
[IKEY:A_BUILDING] - Interact with a building, furniture or mechanism.
[B]
[IKEY:A_CENTER] - Center screen on yourself.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INV_WEAR] - Wear an item.
[B]
[IKEY:A_ACTION] - Create an object or butcher a corpse.
[B]
[IKEY:A_STATUS] - Status.
[B]
[B]
[IKEY:A_ATTACK] - Aim an attack/wrestle.
[B]
[IKEY:A_COMBAT] - Combat preferences.
[B]
[IKEY:A_DATE] - Date/time.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INTERACT] - Interact with an object in an advanced way.
[B]
[IKEY:A_SEARCH] - Search the nearby area very carefully.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TEMPERATURE] - Temperature.
[B]
[IKEY:A_LOG] - Adventure log (tasks, map, etc.).
[B]
[IKEY:A_SNEAK] - Sneak.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL] - Travel.
[B]
[IKEY:A_WEATHER] - Weather.
[B]
[IKEY:A_SLEEP] - Sleep/wait.
[B]
[B][B]
[C:7:0:1]Travel Keys:[C:7:0:0]
[B]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UP]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWN]
[IKEY:CURSOR_LEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_RIGHT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UPLEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UPRIGHT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWNLEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWNRIGHT] - Move.
[B]
[IKEY:A_END_TRAVEL] - Visit location.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL_CLOUDS] - Start/stop cloud viewing.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL_HIDE_INSTRUCTIONS] - Display/hide instructions.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL_MAP] - Display/hide map.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL_LOG] - Adventure log.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL_SLEEP] - Sleep/wait.
